    "# 模块2：数据可视化分析教学\n",
    "---\n",
    "## 🎯 学习目标\n",
    "学完本模块你将能够：\n",
    "- 熟练使用matplotlib和seaborn绘制常见的数据分析图表\n",
    "- 掌握中文显示、绘图风格配置等基础设置\n",
    "- 能够绘制行为时序趋势图、转化漏斗图等电商场景常用图表\n",
    "- 学会从可视化结果中挖掘业务洞察，指导后续特征工程和建模"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 📚 知识点讲解：数据可视化基础\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. 为什么要做数据可视化？\n",
    "人脑对视觉信息的处理速度是文字的6万倍，可视化能够：\n",
    "- 快速发现数据中的规律和异常（比如双十二的峰值）\n",
    "- 直观展示转化漏斗、时序趋势等业务特征\n",
    "- 帮助我们理解用户行为模式，为特征工程提供灵感\n",
    "- 更清晰地向他人展示分析结果\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2. 常用可视化库介绍\n",
    "| 库 | 特点 | 适用场景 |\n",
    "|-----|------|----------|\n",
    "| matplotlib | Python最基础的绘图库，高度可定制 | 各类基础图表绘制 |\n",
    "| seaborn | 基于matplotlib封装，语法更简洁，默认风格更美观 | 统计图表、热力图、分布图等 |\n",
    "| plotly | 交互式图表库，支持鼠标悬停查看详情 | 需要交互探索的场景 |\n",
    "\n",
    "### 3. 电商场景常用可视化类型\n",
    "- **时序趋势图**：展示指标随时间的变化规律\n",
    "- **转化漏斗图**：展示用户从浏览到购买的各环节转化率\n",
    "- **分布直方图**：展示用户行为频次的分布情况\n",
    "- **热力图**：展示不同时段的用户活跃度\n",
    "- **对比柱状图**：对比不同群体的行为差异"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 💻 代码逐行拆解：基础配置与数据加载\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 1. 导入需要的库\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import matplotlib.dates as mdates"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**库说明：**\n",
    "- `matplotlib.pyplot`：matplotlib的pyplot模块，约定俗成缩写为plt\n",
    "- `seaborn`：高级统计绘图库，缩写为sns\n",
    "- `matplotlib.dates`：matplotlib的日期处理模块，用于时间轴的格式化\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 2. 绘图基础配置\n",
    "sns.set(style=\"whitegrid\")  # 设置seaborn绘图风格为白色网格\n",
    "plt.rcParams[\"font.sans-serif\"] = [\"SimHei\"]  # 设置中文字体为黑体，解决中文显示问题\n",
    "plt.rcParams[\"axes.unicode_minus\"] = False  # 解决负号显示为方块的问题"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**参数详解：**\n",
    "- `sns.set(style=\"whitegrid\")`：seaborn的全局风格设置，可选风格：\n",
    "  - `whitegrid`：白色背景+网格线（适合数据分析）\n",
    "  - `darkgrid`：灰色背景+网格线\n",
    "  - `white`：纯白背景\n",
    "  - `dark`：纯灰背景\n",
    "- `plt.rcParams`：matplotlib全局参数配置\n",
    "  - `font.sans-serif`：设置无衬线字体，SimHei是Windows系统自带的黑体\n",
    "  - `axes.unicode_minus`：设置为False可以正常显示负号\n",
    "\n",
    "💡 小技巧：如果是Mac系统，中文字体可以设置为\"PingFang SC\"，Linux系统可以设置为\"WenQuanYi Micro Hei\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 3. 定义文件路径\n",
    "user_file = \"F:/数据分析/project/天池/新人实战/fresh_comp_offline/tianchi_fresh_comp_train_user.csv\"\n",
    "item_file = \"F:/数据分析/project/天池/新人实战/fresh_comp_offline/tianchi_fresh_comp_train_item.csv\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 💻 代码逐行拆解：大数据分块处理技巧\n",
    "\n",
    "由于用户行为表有2300多万行，一次性加载会占用大量内存，我们使用分块处理的方法："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 加载商品子集ID\n",
    "target_items = set(pd.read_csv(item_file)[\"item_id\"])\n",
    "print(f\"✅ 已加载 {len(target_items)} 个目标商品ID\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 分块处理全量用户行为数据\n",
    "chunk_size = 1000000  # 每次处理100万行\n",
    "stats_list = []  # 存储每个块的统计结果\n",
    "\n",
    "for i, chunk in enumerate(pd.read_csv(user_file, chunksize=chunk_size)):\n",
    "    # 只保留需要的列，减少内存占用\n",
    "    chunk = chunk[[\"item_id\", \"behavior_type\", \"time\"]]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 筛选属于目标子集的商品\n",
    "    subset_chunk = chunk[chunk[\"item_id\"].isin(target_items)].copy()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if not subset_chunk.empty:\n",
    "        # 快速提取日期（字符串切片比to_datetime快5倍以上）\n",
    "        subset_chunk[\"date\"] = subset_chunk[\"time\"].str[:10]\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 按日期和行为类型分组统计\n",
    "        daily_stat = subset_chunk.groupby([\"date\", \"behavior_type\"]).size().reset_index(name=\"count\")\n",
    "        stats_list.append(daily_stat)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if (i + 1) % 5 == 0:\n",
    "        print(f\"   已处理 {i + 1} 个块...\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**大数据处理技巧：**\n",
    "1. **分块读取**：`pd.read_csv(chunksize=N)`可以将大文件分成N行一块逐块读取，避免内存不足\n",
    "2. **列裁剪**：只读取需要的列，不要把所有列都加载到内存\n",
    "3. **提前筛选**：在每个块内先筛选需要的数据，再做后续处理，减少后续计算量\n",
    "4. **字符串操作优化**：时间提取用字符串切片`str[:10]`比`pd.to_datetime()`快很多，适合只需要日期的场景\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 合并所有块的统计结果\n",
    "final_stats = pd.concat(stats_list, ignore_index=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 再次聚合，确保同一天的数据不会被拆分到不同块\n",
    "final_stats = final_stats.groupby([\"date\", \"behavior_type\"], as_index=False)[\"count\"].sum()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 数据透视：将行为类型转为列\n",
    "pivot_df = final_stats.pivot(\n",
    "    index=\"date\", \n",
    "    columns=\"behavior_type\", \n",
    "    values=\"count\"\n",
    ").fillna(0)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 重命名列名，方便后续使用\n",
    "pivot_df = pivot_df.rename(\n",
    "    columns={\n",
    "        1: \"look_count\",    # 浏览\n",
    "        2: \"collect_count\", # 收藏\n",
    "        3: \"addcart_count\", # 加购\n",
    "        4: \"buy_count\",     # 购买\n",
    "    }\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 将索引转为日期类型并排序\n",
    "pivot_df.index = pd.to_datetime(pivot_df.index)\n",
    "pivot_df = pivot_df.sort_index()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ 数据处理完成！\")\n",
    "print(pivot_df.head())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**数据透视说明：**\n",
    "- `pivot()`方法可以将长表（long format）转为宽表（wide format）\n",
    "- 长表：每一行是【日期+行为类型+数量】的组合\n",
    "- 宽表：每一行是一个日期，每一列是一种行为类型的数量\n",
    "- 宽表更适合绘图和后续分析\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 💻 代码逐行拆解：时序趋势图绘制\n",
    "\n",
    "我们来绘制四种行为的每日趋势图，重点观察双十二的异常峰值："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "target_date = pd.Timestamp(\"2014-12-12\")  # 双十二日期\n",
    "\n",
    "# 创建4行1列的子图，共享X轴，总大小12*20英寸\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(4, 1, figsize=(12, 20), sharex=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 定义要绘制的指标：(列名, 标题, 颜色)\n",
    "metrics = [\n",
    "    (\"look_count\", \"浏览量 (View)\", \"#3498db\"),     # 蓝色\n",
    "    (\"collect_count\", \"收藏量 (Collect)\", \"#f1c40f\"), # 黄色\n",
    "    (\"addcart_count\", \"加购量 (Add Cart)\", \"#e67e22\"), # 橙色\n",
    "    (\"buy_count\", \"购买量 (Buy)\", \"#e74c3c\"),         # 红色\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "for idx, (col, title, color) in enumerate(metrics):\n",
    "    ax = axes[idx]  # 获取当前子图的坐标轴对象\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 绘制折线图，线宽2.5\n",
    "    ax.plot(pivot_df.index, pivot_df[col], color=color, linewidth=2.5)\n",
    "    # 绘制填充面积，透明度0.2，让趋势更明显\n",
    "    ax.fill_between(pivot_df.index, pivot_df[col], color=color, alpha=0.2)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 标记双十二的位置：红色虚线\n",
    "    ax.axvline(x=target_date, color=\"red\", linestyle=\"--\", linewidth=2, alpha=0.8)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 标注双十二的具体数值\n",
    "    if target_date in pivot_df.index:\n",
    "        val = pivot_df.loc[target_date, col]\n",
    "        ax.text(\n",
    "            target_date, val, f\"  {int(val):,}\",\n",
    "            color=\"red\", fontsize=11, fontweight=\"bold\", va=\"bottom\"\n",
    "        )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 设置子图标题和Y轴标签\n",
    "    ax.set_title(title, fontsize=14, loc=\"left\", fontweight=\"bold\", color=color)\n",
    "    ax.set_ylabel(\"次数\", fontsize=12)\n",
    "    ax.grid(True, linestyle=\"--\", alpha=0.6)  # 显示网格线\n",
    "\n",
    "# 设置X轴格式（只在最后一个子图显示）\n",
    "axes[-1].set_xlabel(\"日期\", fontsize=14)\n",
    "axes[-1].xaxis.set_major_locator(mdates.DayLocator(interval=1))  # 每天一个刻度\n",
    "axes[-1].xaxis.set_major_formatter(mdates.DateFormatter(\"%m-%d\"))  # 日期格式为月-日\n",
    "\n",
    "# 旋转X轴标签，防止重叠\n",
    "plt.setp(axes[-1].get_xticklabels(), rotation=45, ha=\"right\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 整体大标题\n",
    "fig.suptitle(\n",
    "    \"商品子集用户行为全链路转化趋势\",\n",
    "    fontsize=20, fontweight=\"bold\", y=0.995\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 调整子图间距，防止标题重叠\n",
    "plt.tight_layout(rect=[0, 0.03, 1, 0.95])\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**绘图参数详解：**\n",
    "1. **子图创建**：`plt.subplots(rows, cols, figsize=(w, h), sharex=True)`\n",
    "   - `sharex=True`：所有子图共享X轴，避免重复显示日期标签\n",
    "   - `figsize=(w, h)`：整个图的大小，单位是英寸\n",
    "   \n",
    "2. **折线图**：`ax.plot(x, y, color=颜色, linewidth=线宽)`\n",
    "3. **填充面积**：`ax.fill_between(x, y, color=颜色, alpha=透明度)`\n",
    "4. **辅助线**：`ax.axvline(x=位置, color=颜色, linestyle=线型)`，垂直线；`ax.axhline()`是水平线\n",
    "5. **文本标注**：`ax.text(x, y, 文本内容, 其他参数)`，在指定位置添加文本\n",
    "6. **日期格式化**：`mdates.DateFormatter(\"%m-%d\")`，常用格式符：\n",
    "   - `%Y`：4位年份，`%m`：2位月份，`%d`：2位日期\n",
    "   - `%H`：2位小时，`%M`：2位分钟，`%S`：2位秒\n",
    "\n",
    "**结果解读：**\n",
    "- 可以明显看到双十二当天四种行为都出现了异常峰值，尤其是购买量是平日的3-4倍\n",
    "- 浏览、加购、收藏的趋势和购买趋势高度相关，符合业务直觉\n",
    "- 整体趋势平稳，除了双十二没有其他明显异常\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 💻 代码逐行拆解：转化漏斗图绘制\n",
    "\n",
    "转化漏斗是电商场景最常用的图表之一，展示用户从浏览到购买的各环节流失情况："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 计算全周期各行为的总量\n",
    "total_look = pivot_df[\"look_count\"].sum()\n",
    "total_collect = pivot_df[\"collect_count\"].sum()\n",
    "total_addcart = pivot_df[\"addcart_count\"].sum()\n",
    "total_buy = pivot_df[\"buy_count\"].sum()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 漏斗数据\n",
    "funnel_data = [\n",
    "    (\"浏览\", total_look, \"#3498db\"),\n",
    "    (\"收藏\", total_collect, \"#f1c40f\"),\n",
    "    (\"加购\", total_addcart, \"#e67e22\"),\n",
    "    (\"购买\", total_buy, \"#e74c3c\"),\n",
    ]\n",
    "\n",
    "# 计算各环节转化率\n",
    "conversion_rates = []\n",
    "for i in range(len(funnel_data)):\n",
    "    if i == 0:\n",
    "        rate = 100.0\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        rate = (funnel_data[i][1] / funnel_data[i-1][1]) * 100\n",
    "    conversion_rates.append(rate)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 绘制漏斗图\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 8))\n",
    "\n",
    "y_pos = range(len(funnel_data))\n",
    "values = [x[1] for x in funnel_data]\n",
    "labels = [x[0] for x in funnel_data]\n",
    "colors = [x[2] for x in funnel_data]\n",
    "\n",
    "# 绘制横向柱状图\n",
    "bars = ax.barh(y_pos, values, color=colors, height=0.7)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 添加数值和转化率标注\n",
    "for i, bar in enumerate(bars):\n",
    "    width = bar.get_width()\n",
    "    # 标注数值\n",
    "    ax.text(width, bar.get_y() + bar.get_height()/2,\n",
    "            f\" {int(width):,} ({conversion_rates[i]:.1f}%)\",\n",
    "            va=\"center\", fontsize=12, fontweight=\"bold\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 设置Y轴标签\n",
    "ax.set_yticks(y_pos)\n",
    "ax.set_yticklabels(labels, fontsize=12)\n",
    "ax.invert_yaxis()  # 反转Y轴，让浏览在最上面\n",
    "\n",
    "# 隐藏X轴\n",
    "ax.set_xticks([])\n",
    "ax.spines[['top', 'right', 'bottom', 'left']].set_visible(False)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 标题\n",
    "ax.set_title(\"用户行为转化漏斗\", fontsize=18, fontweight=\"bold\", pad=20)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**结果解读：**\n",
    "- 从浏览到收藏的转化率约为1.7%，从收藏到加购约为170%（因为很多用户加购前不收藏）\n",
    "- 从加购到购买的转化率约为41%，说明加购是非常强的购买信号\n",
    "- 整体从浏览到购买的转化率约为1.2%，符合电商行业的正常水平\n",
    "- 这个转化数据对我们后续特征工程非常有指导意义：加购行为的权重应该远高于浏览行为\n"
   ]
  },
  {
